1. Check out code
2. Config base path at system/application/config/config.php and .htaccess
3. Config db at system/application/config/database.php
4. Create database and tables by import gfx.sql.gz
5. INSERT INTO `users` SET `name` = 'foxmosa', `id` = 1;
6. sudo chown www-data:www-data useravatars system/cache (or chmod 777 if you cannot sudo)

On Production Site:
1. Change $route['scaffolding_trigger']  to empty string in system/application/config/routes.php
2. Change error_reporting(E_ALL) to error_reporting(E_ERROR) in ./index.php